CMLFlightPosition Class Reference

Class CMLFlightPosition class objects provide an update on the flight position of a previously spawned aircraft whether in the air or on the ground. In order to ensure that the updates can be applied to the current aircraft the appropriate key attributes such as acid and tailNumber need to match the corresponding current active aircraft. This matching of key attributes applies to all updates against current aircraft. More...

Detailed Description

Class CMLFlightPosition class objects provide an update on the flight position of a previously spawned aircraft whether in the air or on the ground. In order to ensure that the updates can be applied to the current aircraft the appropriate key attributes such as acid and tailNumber need to match the corresponding current active aircraft. This matching of key attributes applies to all updates against current aircraft.
